Sir, your dishes are not very clean.

24
00:03:43,760 --> 00:03:45,760
Sir, what's wrong?

25
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:47,320
Your dishes are spoiled.

26
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:48,600
