29
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:56,079
What do you mean?

30
00:03:56,079 --> 00:03:57,680
Nothing.

31
00:03:58,760 --> 00:03:59,960
What did you say?

32
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:02,160
Don't go.

33
