We haven't paid yet.

34
00:04:03,760 --> 00:04:06,720
Are you looking down on us?

35
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:07,760
Gentlemen,

36
00:04:07,760 --> 00:04:09,960
It's not easy for me to do this small business.

37
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:12,040
Why don't you pay

38
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:12,960
