42
00:04:30,840 --> 00:04:31,680
Sanniang.

43
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:51,040
Be careful.

44
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,760
You're too young to learn well.

45
00:04:58,760 --> 00:05:00,720
You, you, and you.

46
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,680
Leave now.

47
