Sanniang, are you thirsty?

48
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:34,000
Sir. Sir.

49
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,280
You promised.

50
00:05:35,320 --> 00:05:38,520
I'll pay my salary after I finish this knock-off.

51
00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:41,960
Otherwise, my family will starve to death.

52
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:44,360
Give me your salary.

53
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:46,200
Please.

54
00:05:46,280 --> 00:05:47,080
Marry me.

55
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:49,360
Please. Please.

56
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,720
Madam. Madam.

57
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:58,040
Boss.

58
00:05:58,159 --> 00:05:59,960
